name: DSH Mongolian Kinky Curly Hair Lace Closure
description: The DSH Mongolian Kinky Curly Lace Closures are placed on your crown area to blend right in with your hair extensions. These closure hair pieces are easy to maintain and style and can be parted in any direction.The Cuticle is fully intact and the color is still in its virgin state which keeps the integrity of the hair despite the kinky texture and ensures longevity. This 4X4 piece has the ability and versatility to be colored and styled to your preference while returning back to its curly state.

name: DSH Mongolian Kinky Curly Hair
description: The DSH Mongolian kinky curly has a tighter curl with a low luster and coarse texture.Mongolian Hair is a blend of Indian and Chinese Hair. It is less fragile than Indian Hair but not as heavy as Chinese Hair. The DSH Mongolian Kinky Curly hair is 100% Mongolian Virgin hair which has been steamed to match perfectly with Virgin and chemically textured African American hair. *Please note constant heat will slightly loosen the curl Once washed the curls return. This Kinky Curly has been steamed, not chemically processed, to maintain this long lasting texture. Hair it usually lasts longer and Color: Naturally Off Black Weight: Approximately 3.5oz/100g

name: DSH Tropical Curl Lace Closure
description: The DSH Tropical Curl Lace Closure is made out of a 4X4 piece 100% virgin human Brazilian Curly hair. Brazilian Curly has a defined curl pattern and is ideal for natural curly styling. Brazilian Curly comes in it's natural dark brown/black color. This hair can be dyed and straightened. Hair weighs between 3.7-4.0 oz. Top lace Closures pieces are used to close your weave, add instant volume, length and style to thinning hair in just minutes with any of these top Hairpieces that come in human hair

name: DSH Lace Frontal
description:
Our DSH Brazilian Straight and body wave lace frontals can be used to close sew-in weaves across the front hairline or can be blended with natural hair.
Our stock frontals come in basic colors (1b and natural (undyed)).
Be sure to seal your frontal. 
Stock frontals made of hair types, range from 12"-18"  13X4 length
Categories range from Indian, Brazilian, Peruvian and Malaysian

name: DSH Lace Closure
description: DSH Closure pieces are used to close your weave, and allows the wearer to have the versatility of creating a part where they want it to be. This closure piece can be used again and again. It comes in lengths 12"-18"   4 x 3.5 and ranges from brazilian, peruvian, malaysian and indian hair. Knots have not been bleached.

name: Brazilian Body Wave
description:
This is our top selling hair. Wear our natural waves of 100% Virgin Brazilian wavy hair. This hair has volume, low shedding and Wear this hair in its natural wavy pattern or press it straight. Machine Weft.The hair can be dyed to lighter shades, just as you would color any hair.

*Each bundle is approximately 3.5 - 4 oz. and come in a natural dark brown hair color

name: Indian Body Wave
description:
DSH Indian virgin hair is truly the most versatile, exceptional hair. . Naturally full and bouncy, the texture is silky soft with subtle waves and can be easily be curled,straightened, waved, or slashed styled.
Less coarse than Chinese hair, it does not tangle or shed excessively or loose its luster. It is easily matched with any hair texture. comes in natural dark brown color and weighs between 3.5-4.0 z

name: Malaysian Straight Hair
description:
DSH Malaysian hair is sleek and straight. It moves and flows freely and holds curls well even though it is heavy, thick, and dense. Malaysian is not as shiny as Indian hair, yet the texture feels very soft and smooth with lots of body. 
The hair dries straight with a slight wave, which can be flat ironed or set with rollers when wet for a curly or wavy look. 3.5- 4.0 oz .It can be dyed and also has low shedding
